title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Deathmoon
itunes:title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Deathmoon
description:
When you think of movies filmed in Hawaii, you probably think of vacation flicks and dramas, but has the Aloha state ever given us a werewolf film? Yep, in this episode of Weirdhouse Cinema, Rob and Joe watch 1978’s “Deathmoon” starring Robert Foxworth.
